quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  10,104,dir O popol vi hav any dub my religi mi ne worship ki vi worship DI! Mi worship DI sol; Unu terminate your viv Mi komand est believer
  10,105,Mi komand Keep devoted al religi monotheism vi ne practice idol worship
  10,106,Vi ne worship DI ki ne posed potenc benefit vi harm vi! Vi do vi est transgressor
  10,107,Di tusx vi hardship neniom relieve gxi escept Li. Kaj when Li ben vi neni force prevent His grace Li bestows gxi whomever Li chooses His servants. Li est Forgiver Merciful
  10,108,Proklam O popol truth ven vi herein your Lord Whoever direkt direkt his own bon whoever ir astray ir astray his own detriment! Mi ne est guardian over vi
  10,109,Sekv ki revealed vi est pacient DI issues His judgment Li est bon jugx